700062f-a.title: Bronx: 137th Street (East) - Cypress Avenue
700062f-a.text:
675 to 681 (left to right) East 137th Street, north side, east of the N.E. corner of Cypress Ave. The 2-story frame house, set back behind the bushes on the right, bears No. 68l. The barn between the two
houses has no number indicated.
About 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
